titles.title: A bill to reduce temporarily the rate of duty on Methyl N-(2-[[1-(4-chlorophenyl)-1H-pyrazol-3-yl]-oxymethyl] phenyl)-N-methoxycarbanose.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/28/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to reduce temporarily the duty on methyl N-(2-[[1-(4-chlorophenyl)-1H-pyrazol-3-yl]-oxymethyl] phenyl)-N-methoxycarbanose.
